{"tid":776231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上一代住公屋呢一代脱貧發圍真係好難","createTime":"2018-08-11T23:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T07:15:42.000Z","uid":126036,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"92d5b603aff1d723fba62e79adf3273795880f6b","tid":776231,"uid":126036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T23:09:04.000Z","msg":"上一代父母教育水平低，唔識教無好環境比下一代，天生天養再加廢老心態已經輸在起跑線。<br />\n<br />\n呢一代就算再叻再勤力，比你大學畢業撈幾年揾3皮一個月都係好基本既收入。<br />\n<br />\n無父母幹就算死慳死抵都唔洗諗上樓。而你背景得間租緊既公屋，仲要問你比家用。<br />\n<br />\n窮真係會世襲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果上一代係私樓，再按上車根本無難道。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再信得公屋贏天下理論。除非你甘心下一代同你一樣做廢人。"},{"pid":"b22315d57af3f2a6d2102f1bc7876294670cf613","tid":776231,"uid":41803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T23:35:19.000Z","msg":"如果上一代本身已經廢，仲無埋公屋，下一代會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有公屋都起碼有低價租金頂到你搬出去果日<br />\n<br />\n無公屋你自細住邊？屋企花多幾多錢落租金？<br />\n<br />\n用筆錢補習讀書點都好少少，甚至全家買野食起碼營養好少少掛？"},{"pid":"1518011c84f2455b924c9fe30dc6ca5d11dee1fc","tid":776231,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"有公屋咪幾好<br />\n大把人住劏房"},{"pid":"a03757cf5086732e8a2fa922dddc21568aab2e6b","tid":776231,"uid":153114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"男地盤、 紀律部隊<br />\n女 護士"},{"pid":"bc69df15cd42385ef8af1d95689d02f5994b8721","tid":776231,"uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a03757cf5086732e8a2fa922dddc21568aab2e6b","tid":776231,"uid":153114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"男地盤、 紀律部隊<br />\n女 護士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"女：雞"},{"pid":"19f0d4a373fa4b4b4c675a54bbd7a1ea8f43afef","tid":776231,"uid":745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"十萬都難存啦<br />\n但人地一開波就一千萬私樓揸手<br />\n唔係好難 係無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a3cddbf8704d923f1ab92a95bc47b790d632e4","tid":776231,"uid":153114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc69df15cd42385ef8af1d95689d02f5994b8721","tid":776231,"uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a03757cf5086732e8a2fa922dddc21568aab2e6b","tid":776231,"uid":153114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"男地盤、 紀律部隊<br />\n女 護士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"女：雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fdfc566cf9116bd6ee7daf202b16d9d36b67c6","tid":776231,"uid":153114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a03757cf5086732e8a2fa922dddc21568aab2e6b","tid":776231,"uid":153114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"男地盤、 紀律部隊<br />\n女 護士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"搵個一樣職業嘅伴侶已經近6萬fg 10年後10萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c045ad3a09a8e573dccd262ec580c33596e10f2","tid":776231,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"護士係淫啫，唔係雞"},{"pid":"3548285ad0e1da3cfc3bcfe82e77a95bbe94335d","tid":776231,"uid":42079,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"上進啲咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6204b35dd9e2984c4e83748a7083397b6648182a","tid":776231,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c045ad3a09a8e573dccd262ec580c33596e10f2","tid":776231,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"護士係淫啫，唔係雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"幾時有話護士係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係叫啲窮女除咗做護士之外，仲可以做雞"}]}